ref=\"http://eventespresso.com/wiki/wp-user-integration/#ee4-my-events\" rel=\"nofollow\">the documentation page for the WP User Integration add-on</a>.</p>\n						\n					\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Josh\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n\n					\n\n					\n					\n				\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://eventespresso.com/topic/status-of-ee4-add-on-compatibility/#post-80697\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Status of EE4 add-on compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://eventespresso.com/topic/status-of-ee4-add-on-compatibility/#post-80697\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 17 Feb 2014 15:53:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3159:\"\n						\n						<p>Hi everyone!</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ll be posting to this thread with updates when Event Espresso 4-ready add-ons are released. <strong>As of August 17, 2015 the following add-ons are available for EE4:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New</strong>: <a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-promotions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Promotions &#038; Discount Codes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-multi-event-registration/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Multiple Event Registration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/ee4-events-calendar/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Events Calendar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-mailchimp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 MailChimp Integration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-events-grid-view-template/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Events Grid View Template</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-events-table-view-template/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Events Table View Template</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-infusionsoft/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Infusionsoft Integration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-stripe-gateway/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Stripe Payment Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-ticketing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Printable Tickets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-barcode-scanner/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Ticket Scanning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-ideal-mollie-gateway/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 iDeal Mollie Payment Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/wiki/event-espresso-4-roles-permissions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Roles &amp; Capabilities</a> (built into core and replaces the EE3 Roles &amp; Permissions add-on)</li>\n<li><a title=\"Event Espresso WP User Integration\" href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-wp-user-integration/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 WP User Integration</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Event Espresso social sharing\" href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-events-social-sharing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Events Social Sharing</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Event Espresso Sage Pay payment gateway\" href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-sage-pay-gateway/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Sage Pay Payment Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/eventespresso/eea-rest-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 REST API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-people-addon/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 People Add-on</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-vanco-payment-method/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Vanco Payment Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/product/eea-authorizenet-sim/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EE4 Authorize.Net SIM Payment Gateway</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>We welcome your feedback on which add-ons are most important to you. We&#8217;ve set up a survey where you can let us know which add-ons you would like to see ported over to Event Espresso 4 first. Here&#8217;s a link to that survey:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://eventespresso.com/ee4-add-ons-feature-requests/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://eventespresso.com/ee4-add-ons-feature-requests/</a></p>\n						\n					\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Josh\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:55:\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/EventEspresso-Announcements\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:3:\"hub\";s:4:\"href\";s:32:\"http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:4:\"info\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"uri\";s:27:\"eventespre